{"tid":1178213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港靠你班連登仔真係識得屎","createTime":"2019-05-30T09:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T09:38:14.000Z","uid":204126,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d16e05229c6eebd57582b77075001f60e1cb02","tid":1178213,"uid":204126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"唔係針對曬全班連登仔 淨係針對99%人哋<br />\n<br />\n講乜就信乜嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個post入面 講到乜春羅氏校長想報警<br />\n<br />\n拉鳩曬所有聯署反送中嘅師生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千鳩幾<br />\n<br />\n個好評, 而下面都俾屌鳩校長嘅留言佔<br />\n<br />\n據。 係得極少部分嘅人 發現樓主係標題<br />\n<br />\n黨。<br />\n<br />\n而事實係有人冒簽校長佢先話要報警。<br />\n<br />\n我當你唔知呢件事 但下面已經寫到明係<br />\n<br />\n因為冒簽而報警,有哂因果關係,而唔係因<br />\n<br />\n有人聯署要報警, 另外就我所見係冇任何<br />\n<br />\n一個老師有作出聯署嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班連登仔一見到疑似敵人就扯撚曬旗<br />\n<br />\n狗衝, 喪失理性思考能力, 標題寫乜就信<br />\n<br />\n乜, 香港真係多得有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:反送中<br />\n<br />\n保良局羅氏基金中學聲明報警拉聯署師生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1177910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1177910</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b12693dffc719b7b93330244b4dbd62a4524ad3c","tid":1178213,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"每個小人物都可以有佢嘅作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=UJpThwxvwmp